    public class DBAnnotationViewerMain
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    Main Annotation Viewer GUI. Allows user to choose directory of XCAS or XMI files, then launches the AnnotationViewerDialog. copied from AnnotationViewerMain. Modified to load CAS from database.
